Invocation Name: midland states bank
des:
You can now stay on top of your finances with the Midland States Bank skill. You can ask Alexa for balances and recent transactions. Once you've enabled the skill, you can ask such questions as: - What's my checking account balance? - What are my recent transactions? - What are my account balances?

Use of this skill will allow financial information to be read aloud and/or displayed visually.
